data.description: VA Qualified ASSUMPTION!  You do not have to be a veteran to assume this loan. Current rate 4.25%, approximately $430k balance.  This home is nearly new with all of the shiny new finishes along with landscaping, corner lot, fencing and window coverings already installed in family friendly Crystal Valley Ranch.  2-story living with a three car garage, four bedrooms and a loft up, and an open concept Great Room layout on the main floor.  Large covered outdoor patio that is accessed through the double glass doors in the Kitchen/dining area.  Great for entertaining.  Crystal Valley Ranch has a Clubhouse, fitness center, park, a playground and a pool, with food trucks and events, all within a 10 minute drive to downtown Castle Rock.  Convenient to Colorado Springs and the Denver Tech Center.  Large Crawl space for extra storage.  There will be an open house Saturday 8/26/23 from 12pm-3pm
